HEADWORD: Lady-killing
<hw>La"dy-kill`ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The art or practice of
captivating the hearts of women.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Better for the sake of womankind that this dangerous dog should
leave off <qex>lady-killing</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Thackeray.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

